name: Thank you for not surfing
description:
Thank you for not surfing
by Andreas Linnell

Limited edition of 20.

Printed with archival grade Vivera pigment inks on acid free, Italian cold press Eterna Elegant Fine Art 320 GSM. Both inks and paper are archival grade.

Dimensions: 59,4 x 42 cm

Each print comes signed and numbered by the artist.

name: Helvetica Regular
description:
